{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/javascript/event-flow/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Kooku's log","author":"Kooku","siteUrl":"https://kooku.netlify.com","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"koomg9599/kooku-s-log"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"kooku"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"e1a61fee-5620-5761-84fb-04f7d4056921","excerpt":"자바스크립트에서 중요한 Event Flow에 대하여 알아보자! 대부분 Event Bubble은 알고 있을 것 입니다. React에서는 이를 막기 위해 을 사용한 경험이 많을 것 입니다. 하지만 Event Flow에는 Event Bubble말고도 다른 것들이 있다는 사실을 아시나요? 이번에는 Event Flow에 대하여 완벽하게 다루어 보겠습니다. 들어가기 전에 Event에는 3단계의 life cycle이 존재합니다. (cycle, target, bubbling…","html":"<p>자바스크립트에서 중요한 <strong>Event Flow</strong>에 대하여 알아보자! 대부분 <em>Event Bubble</em>은 알고 있을 것 입니다. React에서는 이를 막기 위해 <code class=\"language-text\">event.stopPropagation()</code>을 사용한 경험이 많을 것 입니다. 하지만 <strong>Event Flow</strong>에는 <em>Event Bubble</em>말고도 다른 것들이 있다는 사실을 아시나요? 이번에는 <strong>Event Flow</strong>에 대하여 완벽하게 다루어 보겠습니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"들어가기-전에\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%93%A4%EC%96%B4%EA%B0%80%EA%B8%B0-%EC%A0%84%EC%97%90\" aria-label=\"들어가기 전에 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>들어가기 전에</h2>\n<p>Event에는 3단계의 life cycle이 존재합니다. (cycle, target, bubbling)\n웹페이지에서 이벤트를 인식하는 순서는 <strong>Event Flow</strong>라 불리며 이에 대하여 자세히 알아보겠습니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"index\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#index\" aria-label=\"index permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Index</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><strong><a href=\"#1-event-bubble\">Event Bubble</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"#2-event-capturing\">Event Capturing</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"#3-dom-event-flow\">DOM Event Flow</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"#4-%EB%A7%88%EB%AC%B4%EB%A6%AC\">마무리</a></strong></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"1-event-bubble\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-event-bubble\" aria-label=\"1 event bubble permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Event Bubble</h2>\n<p>특정한 element에서 이벤트가 발생했을때 상위 element로 event가 전파해 나가는 것을 <strong>Event Bubbling</strong>이라고 부릅니다.\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"bubbling\" title=\"bubbling\" src=\"/static/0f81a02ca1e28b64ad4082ce60258a62/fcda8/bubbling.png\" srcset=\"/static/0f81a02ca1e28b64ad4082ce60258a62/12f09/bubbling.png 148w,\n/static/0f81a02ca1e28b64ad4082ce60258a62/e4a3f/bubbling.png 295w,\n/static/0f81a02ca1e28b64ad4082ce60258a62/fcda8/bubbling.png 590w,\n/static/0f81a02ca1e28b64ad4082ce60258a62/6114d/bubbling.png 623w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>......<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>demo<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Press here.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>위와 같은 HTML에서 <strong>&#x3C;div></strong>가 클릭되었을 때, 클릭 이벤트는 다음과 같은 순서로 전파되어 집니다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>&#x3C;div></li>\n<li>&#x3C;body></li>\n<li>&#x3C;html></li>\n<li>Document</li>\n</ol>\n<p>가장 먼저 &#x3C;div> 요소를 작동시키고 그 다음엔 DOM tree를 따라 올라가는 것입니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"2-event-capturing\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-event-capturing\" aria-label=\"2 event capturing permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Event Capturing</h2>\n<p>또다른 event flow는 <strong><em>Event Capturing</em></strong>이라고 불리며 Netscape Browser에서 처음 소개되었습니다.\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"capturing\" title=\"capturing\" src=\"/static/82768f588972b8a7380bd91966eac7b2/fcda8/capturing.png\" srcset=\"/static/82768f588972b8a7380bd91966eac7b2/12f09/capturing.png 148w,\n/static/82768f588972b8a7380bd91966eac7b2/e4a3f/capturing.png 295w,\n/static/82768f588972b8a7380bd91966eac7b2/fcda8/capturing.png 590w,\n/static/82768f588972b8a7380bd91966eac7b2/6114d/capturing.png 623w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span>\n그림을 보면 알겠지만 <em>Event Bubbling</em>과는 반대입니다.\n만약 &#x3C;div> 요소가 클릭된다면 이벤트는 다음과 같은 순서로 전파됩니다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Document</li>\n<li>&#x3C;html></li>\n<li>&#x3C;body></li>\n<li>&#x3C;div></li>\n</ol>\n<p><em>Event Capturing</em>은 현대 브라우저에서 지원이 잘 안되므로 특별한 경우 사용하게 됩니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"3-dom-event-flow\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-dom-event-flow\" aria-label=\"3 dom event flow permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. DOM Event Flow</h2>\n<p>표준 <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-3-Events/\">DOM Events</a>에서 event propagation의 3 단계가 있습니다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Capturing phase – the event goes down to the element.</li>\n<li>Target phase – the event reached the target element.</li>\n<li>Bubbling phase – the event bubbles up from the element.</li>\n</ol>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"DOM2 Event Flow\" title=\"DOM2 Event Flow\" src=\"/static/e8a8ec2c26491deb07d9d00709b9343c/fcda8/DOM2_Event_Flow.png\" srcset=\"/static/e8a8ec2c26491deb07d9d00709b9343c/12f09/DOM2_Event_Flow.png 148w,\n/static/e8a8ec2c26491deb07d9d00709b9343c/e4a3f/DOM2_Event_Flow.png 295w,\n/static/e8a8ec2c26491deb07d9d00709b9343c/fcda8/DOM2_Event_Flow.png 590w,\n/static/e8a8ec2c26491deb07d9d00709b9343c/6114d/DOM2_Event_Flow.png 623w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span>\n<p>위의 단계 순서로 <strong>Event Flow</strong>가 발생하는게 원칙이지만 실제로는 3 단계로 발생하지는 않습니다.</p>\n<p>만약 <em>capturing phase</em>를 사용하고 싶다면 handler <code class=\"language-text\">capture</code> 옵션을 <code class=\"language-text\">true</code>로 변경해야합니다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">capture</code> 옵션에는 두가지 값이 들어갈 수 있습니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>만약 <code class=\"language-text\">false</code> (default)라면, handler는 <em>bubbling phase</em>를 실행합니다.</li>\n<li>만약 <code class=\"language-text\">true</code> 라면, handler는 <em>capturing phase</em>를 실행하게 됩니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>예제 코드는 다음과 같습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Example: Setting Event Handling using DOM<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text/css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n      <span class=\"token selector\">html</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #fff<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token selector\">body</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Verdana<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #7e7e<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #fff<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 4px solid #555<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Verdana<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #fa8b7c<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #fff<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 4px solid #555<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    body tag\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      p tag\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> elem <span class=\"token keyword\">of</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelectorAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'*'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      elem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">'click'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token parameter\">e</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">Capturing: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>elem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>tagName<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n      elem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'click'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">e</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span>\n        console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">Bubbling: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>elem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>tagName<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>p 태그 클릭시 Event Flow</p>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"event flow\" title=\"event flow\" src=\"/static/d79ddb90c348f61c1a1707882de22b8c/1c72d/event-flow.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/d79ddb90c348f61c1a1707882de22b8c/a80bd/event-flow.jpg 148w,\n/static/d79ddb90c348f61c1a1707882de22b8c/1c91a/event-flow.jpg 295w,\n/static/d79ddb90c348f61c1a1707882de22b8c/1c72d/event-flow.jpg 590w,\n/static/d79ddb90c348f61c1a1707882de22b8c/a8a14/event-flow.jpg 885w,\n/static/d79ddb90c348f61c1a1707882de22b8c/d412e/event-flow.jpg 947w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-alig